installing all package in one file:
----------------------------------
create package list file  (ex :requirements.txtit containts all packages names)
and run in CLI >  pip install -r requirements.txt
Note:
to Export packages installed in python to requierements.txt------> pip freeze > requirements.txt  (with versions)
							                                                ------> pip list > requirements.txt  (with out versions)

install in spyder:
------------------
To install spyder editor>> pip install spyder 
To active spyder editor >> python -m spyder.app.start
TO open spyder >> spyder3 


